	dprr:hasNoteText "Pr. 44. See MRR 2.322, and Index, 632, and delete the query. On his tribe and origin, see Syme, Historia 13, 1964, 320-321; Wiseman, NM 270, no. 469.\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5964> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5964" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Like Piso (see above) he was allotted a province in the Senate meeting on November 28, and submitted to the Senate's later annulment of the action (Cic. Phil. 3.25)." .
